    <item>
      <title>特朗普考虑挑战限制其支出权力的法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/white-house-eyes-fight-with-congress-courts-over-spending-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻社看到的一份文件显示，白宫正在考虑挑战一项已有 50 年历史的法律的合宪性，该法律限制了总统对联邦支出的控制、放松了公务员的解雇、限制了薪酬并控制了独立机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/white-house-eyes-fight-with-congress-courts-over-spending-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 20:33:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普签署莱肯·莱利法案，针对被指控犯罪的移民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-signs-laken-riley-act-targeting-migrants-accused-of-crimes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普周三签署了《莱肯·莱利法案》，旨在打击被指控犯罪的移民，特朗普称这是其政府承诺对无证移民和边境安全采取更严厉措施的核心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-signs-laken-riley-act-targeting-migrants-accused-of-crimes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 19:59:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢特尼克称特朗普的关税将恢复美国经济和尊重</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/lutnick-says-mexico-canada-can-avoid-tariffs-with-border-action</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普提名的商务部长霍华德·卢特尼克 (Howard Lutnick) 在确认听证会上为关税问题做出了详细的辩护，这是迄今为止内阁人选发出的最明确信号，表明新政府准备对盟友和对手征收关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/lutnick-says-mexico-canada-can-avoid-tariffs-with-border-action</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 17:26:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划将关塔那摩军事监狱用于关押移民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-revokes-biden-s-extended-protections-for-venezuelans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他正在签署一项行政命令，要求五角大楼和国土安全部研究在关塔那摩湾海军基地建立一个可容纳多达 30,000 名无证移民的设施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-revokes-biden-s-extended-protections-for-venezuelans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 14:41:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
